### Image Details
- **File Name**: `odin-lined.png`
- **Style**: Black outline (lined/stroke) version of the Odin logo
- **Design**: Stylized "ODIN" text in a bold, Viking/Norse-inspired font with clean black lines on transparent background
- **Purpose**: Left sidebar mein **logo** ke roop mein use hota hai (Unsplash fern image ke upar white color mein ya dark overlay ke saath)
- **Why "lined"?** Yeh solid fill version nahi, sirf outline (stroke) wala clean version hai taaki dark/light backgrounds pe achhe se dikhe aur text shadow ke saath sundar lage.

### How to Use in Your Project (Recommended)

#### 1. HTML (Sidebar mein logo)
```html
<div class="sidebar">
  <img src="imgs/odin-lined.png" alt="Odin" class="logo">
  
  <!-- Optional tagline -->
  <p class="tagline">This is not a real online service.<br>You won't be able to log in.</p>
</div>
```

#### 2. Best CSS for Logo (Norse feel ke saath)

```css
.sidebar {
  background: url('https://unsplash.com/photos/25xggax4bSA/download?force=true') center/cover no-repeat;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  color: white;
}

.logo {
  width: 180px;           /* Adjust size as needed */
  height: auto;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8));  /* Depth ke liye */
  z-index: 2;
}

/* Agar aap Norse font + text logo chahte ho to yeh use karo (optional) */
